The paper discusses sensitivity analysis for influence diagrams, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and decision making (cs.SY). The methods presented involve computation and optimization, which are also relevant to data science (cs.DS) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with decision making and strategy comparison, which are topics in game theory (cs.GT).
